---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import iconImage from "../../assets/icon.png";
---
<section
  class="h-screen w-full mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center px-4 sm:px-6"
  aria-label="Hero"
>
  <div
    class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1200px] text-center space-y-5 sm:space-y-6 pt-[max(8px,env(safe-area-inset-top))] pb-[max(8px,env(safe-area-inset-bottom))]"
  >
    <h1 class="font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight [text-wrap:balance]">
      <span class="block text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Design the
        <span class="underline decoration-2 sm:decoration-4 decoration-[#3DA9FC]">Convenience</span>.
      </span>
      <span class="block mt-2 text-lg sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
        「便利」を、設計で届ける。
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p
      class="text-[#38434F] mx-auto max-w-[48ch] sm:max-w-3xl leading-relaxed [text-wrap:balance] text-base sm:text-lg"
    >
      Clear words. Clear paths. Clear system.<br class="hidden sm:block" />
      わかる × 速い × 壊れない = 生活が軽くなる。
    </p>

    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 text-sm sm:text-base"
    >
      <span
        class="px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 sm:py-2.5 min-h-[40px] rounded-full border border-[#3DA9FC] leading-none flex items-center"
        >Information Architecture</span
      >
      <span
        class="px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 sm:py-2.5 min-h-[40px] rounded-full border border-[#3DA9FC] leading-none flex items-center"
        >Performance</span
      >
    </div>

    <div class="pt-4 sm:pt-6 flex justify-center">
      <div
        class="w-full max-w-[560px] rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl border-2 sm:border-4 border-[#3DA9FC] bg-white px-4 sm:px-6 py-4 sm:py-5 shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#3DA9FC] sm:shadow-[10px_10px_0_0_#3DA9FC]"
        role="note"
      >
        <div class="flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 items-center text-left">
          <Image
            src={iconImage}
            alt="yumekichiのアイコン"
            class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 sm:ring-4 ring-[#D8EEFE]"
          />
          <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-bold leading-tight text-base sm:text-lg">yumekiti</p>
            <p class="text-[#5F6C7B] text-xs sm:text-sm -mt-0.5">
              Infra × Web Experience
            </p>
            <p class="text-[#38434F] text-xs sm:text-sm mt-2">
              Make it simple. Make it convenient.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
